ecoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: =
#000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">memecoin</a>.=
 I suppose the problem with this is that Trump has a lot of older, less cry=
pto-native fans, and this would not be an effective way to tap them for mon=
ey.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But you can get arbitrarily close to this =E2=
