<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In some ways, if you want to acquire a public =
company in a merger or acquisition, it helps to already own most of the sto=
ck. In other ways that makes it harder. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/34916007.287354/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9maW5hbmNlL=
2ludmVzdGluZy9lbmRlYXZvci1hZ3JlZXMtdG8tYmUtYm91Z2h0LWJ5LXNpbHZlci1sYWtlLWF0=
